<section id="measuring-similarity" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="measuring-similarity">Measuring similarity</h2>
<p>Suppose that we have embeddings for three documents:</p>
<ul>
<li>the petitioner’s argument;</li>
<li>the government’s argument;</li>
<li>the court’s legal reasoning.</li>
</ul>
<p>We can calculate:</p>
<p>[ A_i = (C_i, P_i) - (C_i, G_i) ]</p>
<p>where (C_i) represents the court text, (P_i) represents the petitioner text, and (G_i) represents the government text.</p>


</section>

